<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>{{ title }} — CSPM Blog</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{ excerpt }}">
<meta property="og:title" content="{{ title }} — CSPM">
<meta property="og:description" content="{{ excerpt }}">
<meta property="og:type" content="article">
{% if image %}<meta property="og:image" content="{{ image }}">{% endif %}
<meta name="author" content="Ing. Germán Golder">
<link rel="canonical" href="https://cspm-landing.vercel.app/blog/{{ page.fileSlug }}/">
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "{{ title }}",
  "description": "{{ excerpt }}",
  "datePublished": "{{ date | dateISO }}",
  "author": {
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": "Ing. Germán Golder"
  },
  "publisher": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "CSPM",
    "url": "https://cspm-landing.vercel.app"
  }{% if image %},
  "image": "{{ image }}"{% endif %}
}
</script>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/base.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/nav.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/blog-post.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/cta-footer.css">
</head>
<body>

{% include "nav-blog.njk" %}

<article class="post-article">

  <header class="post-header">
    <div class="post-meta">
      <span class="post-date">{{ date | fechaES }}</span>
      {% if tags %}
      <div class="post-tags">
        {% for tag in tags %}
          <span class="post-tag">{{ tag }}</span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <h1 class="post-title">{{ title }}</h1>
    <p class="post-excerpt">{{ excerpt }}</p>
    {% if image %}
    <div class="post-hero-img">
      <img src="{{ image }}" alt="{{ title }}" loading="eager">
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </header>

  <div class="post-body">
    {{ content | safe }}
  </div>

  <footer class="post-footer">
    <div class="post-author">
      <div class="author-info">
        <div class="author-avatar">GG</div>
        <div>
          <strong>Ing. Germán Golder</strong>
          <span>Fundador · CSPM</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/blog/" class="post-back">← Volver al blog</a>
  </footer>

</article>

<section class="cta-section">
  <h2>¿Tenés activos solares que ya <em>no usás</em>?</h2>
  <p>Contactanos para una evaluación técnica sin compromiso.</p>
  <div class="cta-buttons">
    <a href="mailto:ggoldercspm@gmail.com" class="btn-primary">
      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
      Escribinos
    </a>
    <a href="/blog/" class="btn-secondary btn-outline-dark">Más artículos</a>
  </div>
</section>

{% include "footer-blog.njk" %}

<script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
